    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/7b8d06865a0687626805e6824fc1a923.poster.avif?t=1765931469\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/7b8d06865a0687626805e6824fc1a923.webm?t=1765931469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/7b8d06865a0687626805e6824fc1a923.mp4?t=1765931469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a faraway kingdom, a brave young knight-in-training named Boy prepares for his most incredible adventure yet.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/a041b0d416fb26981e0d8b7619c7304a.poster.avif?t=1765931469\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/a041b0d416fb26981e0d8b7619c7304a.webm?t=1765931469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/a041b0d416fb26981e0d8b7619c7304a.mp4?t=1765931469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boy is determined to defeat the evil that looms over the realm and rescue the beautiful princess who is being held captive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/eab99e336d7597c626e38a1cfe288adf.poster.avif?t=1765931469\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/eab99e336d7597c626e38a1cfe288adf.webm?t=1765931469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/eab99e336d7597c626e38a1cfe288adf.mp4?t=1765931469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will Boy, with his boldness and heroic spirit, be able to overcome the pitfalls of the path and restore peace to the kingdom?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/4f6a377a48dbab6b8df11407719ae3ad.poster.avif?t=1765931469\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/4f6a377a48dbab6b8df11407719ae3ad.webm?t=1765931469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/4f6a377a48dbab6b8df11407719ae3ad.mp4?t=1765931469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fantasy Boy is a 2D platformer where you explore a fantasy world, battle numerous enemies, and most importantly, have FUN!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/65904716bfa0f10ab6f3127defba050a.poster.avif?t=1765931469\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/65904716bfa0f10ab6f3127defba050a.webm?t=1765931469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/65904716bfa0f10ab6f3127defba050a.mp4?t=1765931469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >...and don't forget you can play in co-op with your friends!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/1168b27818badc122c4ca3a152719b46.poster.avif?t=1765931469\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/1168b27818badc122c4ca3a152719b46.webm?t=1765931469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321950/extras/1168b27818badc122c4ca3a152719b46.mp4?t=1765931469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
